| **No 8 Query (as Plain Text)** | **SELECT DISTINCT p.Name  FROM Players p JOIN PlayerPerformance pp ON p.Player\_id \= pp.Player\_id JOIN Teams t ON pp.Team\_id \= t.Team\_id WHERE t.Coach\_id IN (     SELECT Coach\_id      FROM Coaches      WHERE Nationality \= 'Spanish' ) GROUP BY p.Player\_id, p.Name HAVING COUNT(DISTINCT pp.Team\_id) \= (SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT t.Team\_id)                                       FROM Teams t                                       WHERE t.Coach\_id IN (SELECT Coach\_id                                                            FROM Coaches                                                            WHERE Nationality \= 'Spanish'));**  |
